info.description:
PyQe is a small Python script, pyqe.py that uses Tkinter, Python's standard GUI
toolkit, to let the user execute commands from a pre-defined list of commands,
just by entering a few characters. It is designed to be simple and quickly do
the job. It has a listen mode for quicker startups.
info.name: PyQe
info.summary: PyQe is a small and easy-to-use command launcher
